# Morse Trainer Firmware

Firmware for a simple device to learn Kids to type morse code.

## Systems
### Hardware
- Attiny2313
- HD44780 Display
- Piezo
- Switch-Button

### Software
- [Peter Fleury LCD Library](http://tinyurl.com/peterfleury)

